        <h1 data-reveal="delay-1">Maryland<em>Glock Ban</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub" data-reveal="delay-2">
          Maryland's legislature passed SB 334, banning the sale of Glocks and
          all pistols with cruciform trigger bars. The bill targets the internal
          mechanism that enables illegal auto-sear "switch"
          conversion&thinsp;&mdash;&thinsp;and bans the most popular handgun in
          America in the process.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-chips" data-reveal="delay-3">
